Prof. '''Chris Maina Peter''' ([[14 Mata]] [[1954]]) ni Umwarimu w’Amategeko akaba ariwe ukuriye
Komite ishinzwe gufasha mu by’amategeko muri Kaminuza ya [[Dar es Salaam]]. Niwe umaze gusimburwa ku mwanya w’inama y’ubutegetsi ya Kituo Cha katiba akanaba umwe mu bari bagize inama y’ubuetegetsi ya Kituo Cha Katiba. Niwe wari ayoboye Misiyo yo mu Rwanda; YAnditse ku burenganzira bw’ikiremwa muntu n’amategekonshinga mu karere k’Iburasirazuba. Imirimo ye irimo 
''The Goldenberg Affair in Kenya: A Peoples’ Opinion'' (''With Justice Samuel Wako Wambuzi and Prof. Joseph Oloka-Onyango''), 2005; Constitutionalism & Transition: African and Eastern European Perspectives (''wWith Prof. Joseph Oloka-Onyango''), 2004; ''Constitutional Review Process in Kenya: A Report of a Fact-Finding Mission'' (Compiled and Edited with Prof. Edward F. Ssempebwa), 2003 and ''Constitutionalism in East Africa: Progress, Challenges and Prospects'' (''With Kivutha Kibwana and Nyangabyaki Bazaara''). Iyi mirimo yose yakozwe mu rwego rwa Kituo Cha Katiba. <ref>[http://www.kituochakatiba.org/index2.php?option=com_docman&task=doc_view&gid=1199&Itemid=36 Ugushakisha Ukuri n’Ubumuntu, Kituo Cha Katiba, Nyakanga, 2004 – Gashyantare, 2006] </ref>
